{"tid":152014,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔清楚就問]到底壞火牛定死老母板？","createTime":"2017-03-11T11:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T13:04:28.000Z","uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db6bdabdfef765c8bf108276d6ae34ec9013f6c9","tid":152014,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:23:21.000Z","msg":"今朝我搬部機擺去第二個位 ，之後插過啲線就開唔返。<br />\n<br />\n底板 asrock b85mpro4<br />\n火牛 antec neoceoii450<br />\n<br />\n症狀<br />\n火牛風扇唔轉 底板燈唔著<br />\n<br />\n試左幾個方法 睇吓邊到壞<br />\n1. 換左火牛條線 都係唔著 <br />\n2.換拖板 都係唔著<br />\n3.螺絲批開機 都係唔著<br />\n4.short火牛24pin綠線同黑線 著左火牛風扇會轉<br />\n5.換牛試 聽日先借到火牛試<br />\n<br />\n請問係唔係底板出事多？"},{"pid":"4466e739edd4e906e52a517ca0b1cb4b0f866de2","tid":152014,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fe2906b85a92dc80e9089a26b428b2a517777b","tid":152014,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:43:59.000Z","msg":"搬部機點解要插過d 線"},{"pid":"2cb22b131101aa043839620c0945d274291deb21","tid":152014,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搬部機點解要插過d 線</blockquote><br />\n唔係入面個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我指 usb呀 3.5mk DP個啲"},{"pid":"4619bc3bded216153bef0162a35650e04528cb39","tid":152014,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"cpu 風扇著唔著"},{"pid":"72f49a5692776023de27cf3ef38fe7da61e64555","tid":152014,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>cpu 風扇著唔著</blockquote><br />\n唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27bb8c70866a0555f636502e452b7ad2f50514fc","tid":152014,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,